The prom king.

01:08.416 --> 01:10.244
When I was a freshmen,
the curse found my sister.

01:12.072 --> 01:13.812
And when she broke up
with her boyfriend,

01:13.856 --> 01:15.945
just a regular
high school break up,

01:15.988 --> 01:17.251
the kind that everyone
goes through...

01:18.817 --> 01:20.471
that's when the curse came out.

01:20.515 --> 01:22.038
Her boyfriend gets really mad.

01:23.126 --> 01:24.562
He hits her.

01:26.869 --> 01:28.827
But that's not enough for him.

01:28.871 --> 01:31.003
