02:18.007 --> 02:18.834
Dad!

02:20.052 --> 02:21.228
Dad, wake up.

02:22.359 --> 02:23.534
Daddy?

02:27.930 --> 02:30.280
Mike, what are you doing?

02:30.324 --> 02:32.326
