Don't. You can't hurt me.

02:34.589 --> 02:35.764
Dad!

02:37.331 --> 02:39.333
Girls?

02:42.510 --> 02:44.033
Hey, Mike.

02:49.734 --> 02:52.389
Cindy! No!

02:52.433 --> 02:54.086
No!

02:54.130 --> 02:56.872
No! My baby!

02:56.915 --> 02:59.048
My baby!

03:07.230 --> 03:09.667
Then the curse moved again.

03:09.711 --> 03:11.408
I felt it.

03:13.976 --> 03:15.369
I feel it.

03:20.156 --> 03:22.724
Maybe no one else at my high
school knows, but I know.

03:24.291 --> 03:25.944
It's here...

03:25.988 --> 03:27.381
waiting.

03:36.172 --> 03:39.175
Ellie, hey!

03:39.219 --> 03:41.699
Oh my God, you missed it.

03:41.743 --> 03:44.572
Creepy Ben went psycho on Miss Higgins
when she called him out for being late.

03:44.615 --> 03:47.183
It was insane.
Wow, sorry I missed it.

03:47.227 --> 03:49.011
Wow, bitch much?

03:49.054 --> 03:50.752
