to look out there.

18:31.197 --> 18:32.720
Honey?

18:35.375 --> 18:37.942
Ellie?

18:37.986 --> 18:39.944
Maybe it's better if
you stay home today.

18:39.988 --> 18:41.685
They'll understand.
No.

18:43.687 --> 18:45.602
Honey, we've been through
this kind of thing.

18:45.646 --> 18:47.256
I'm gonna go.

18:47.300 --> 18:48.562
I wanna go.

18:48.605 --> 18:50.303
Fine, then I'll drive you.

18:50.346 --> 18:52.000
I told Nicholas I'd go with him.

18:52.043 --> 18:53.741
And you told me Morgan's dad
was going to be home.

18:55.482 --> 18:57.310
I... thought he would be.

19:15.850 --> 19:18.200
<i>♪ Welcome to the end of eras ♪</i>

19:18.244 --> 19:21.812
