20:27.574 --> 20:29.184
I mean, I can't stop
thinking about it.

20:29.228 --> 20:30.925
You were almost
there that night.

20:32.579 --> 20:35.277
It's my fault.
No, don't say that.

20:35.321 --> 20:37.932
